def is_cup_available(cup:item):
    # Check if a given item is a cup
    symbol cup_exists=exists x: item : is_cup(x) and x==cup
    return cup_exists

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind cup: item where:
            is_cup(cup)

        # Determine if any of the found cups is suitable for brewing coffee
        foreach cup: item:
            if is_cup_available(cup) and not inhand(cup):
                # An available cup is found The next step is to ensure the cup is grasped without er
ror
                achieve_once inhand(cup)

        bind coffee_maker: item where:
            is_coffe_maker(coffee_maker)
        # Approach and switch on the coffee maker to start brewing a cup of coffee
        achieve close_char(char, coffee_maker) and is_on(coffee_maker)
